{"type":null,"faqId":45785,"title":"荣耀小K与手机无法配对或者无法连接手机怎么办？","answer":"<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">请先确认无法配对具体情况，是扫描二维码失败，还是登陆后界面呈灰色、提示未连接。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><strong>扫描二维码失败</strong></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1.确认手表版本，若手表软件版本为1.35.4.X以下版本，请用户通过花粉论坛指导帖一键升级至1.35.4.X版本后再进行配对。一键升级指导链接：<a href=\"http://cn.club.vmall.com/thread-6620036-1-1.html\">http://cn.club.vmall.com/thread-6620036-1-1.html</a>若扫描二维码时周围环境光线太强、太暗或2G网络不稳定，请打开窗户或在室外信号较好的地方进行扫描 ；</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2.如果扫描二维码时提示正在初始化，说明手表首次启动，请等待1分钟后再重试。如果始终扫描不上，首先看小K的时间是否更新，一般来说时间同步之后就能扫描二维码了；如果时间一直不同步，则需要确认SIM卡业务是否正常，</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">非常重要：<?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;SIM卡需开通【2G数据流量业务】、【短信业务】及【来电显示业务】。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;深圳、上海及部分地区2G数据业务默认不开通，需要用户拨打10086开通。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10086电话沟通话术：<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;告知10086SIM卡放在手机上可以上网，但放在儿童电话手表上无法上网，儿童智能手表只支持2G上网，请10086帮忙开通上网功能。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">若是刚插入SIM卡扫描二维码，则需要长按手表侧键10s重启手表，重启以后等待几分钟，待手表时间准确后方能扫描二维码。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;如果扫描二维码后，无法收到验证码或说到验证码为乱码，需确认：<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;是否开通短信业务，<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入的号码为手表的号码而非手机号码，<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">−&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SIM卡为实名制卡，如果为非实名制卡，请用户进行实名制认证。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">PS：新规定，SIM卡实名制，短信等功能被屏蔽。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;确保周围有GSM网络，在窗口边、室外等开阔地方尝试。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;检查一下手机摄像头是否有脏污，或者换个摄像头更高清一点的手机。请更换手机再尝试操作，确保非手机像素太低导致；<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">确认业务是否开通正确方法：<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp;请确认手表SIM卡里的短信功能是否正常：可以将SIM卡放在手机里尝试是否可以收发短信，建议致电SIM卡运营商客服确认短信收发业务开通 。<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp;请确认SIM卡是否开通了2G数据流量业务： 由于手表使用的是2G网络，建议直接拨打10086开通2G GPRS数据业务（注：深圳及部分地区2G数据业务默认不开通，需联系运营商开通)<o:p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" align></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><strong>APP登录界面呈灰色</strong></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">APP页面功能键呈灰色无法使用，为什么？</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">若是第一次绑定手表，APP页面是灰色的，所有功能也无法使用：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">可能是是数据与云服务同步发生延迟，请等待一段时间。同时检查SIM卡在手机上2G(GPRS)上网功能是否正常，或者打电话给移动运营商咨询。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">若之前已经绑定过，登录之后，APP是灰色的：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1.建议分别用微信、QQ、华为账号来登录一下。用户一般的情况下第一次会选用微信或QQ，第二次会习惯用自己手机号对应的华为账号登陆），基本上是能找回原先的小K的；</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">PS：（重要）遇到APP界面为灰色的情况，通常都是账号登陆错误导致，请用户将华为穿戴、QQ、微信、微博账号分别尝试。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">切换账号可以按以下步骤操作：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">第一步，点击右上角个人信息</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105300072163123776=\"97\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7c_8zod1.jpg\"><img width=\"255\" height=\"408\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7c_8zod1.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">第二步，点击下方退出登录</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105300072163123776=\"98\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7d_qf3c6.jpg\"><img width=\"258\" height=\"412\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7d_qf3c6.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">第三步，注销当前账号</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105300072163123776=\"99\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7e_daytr.jpg\"><img width=\"258\" height=\"417\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7e_daytr.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">第四步，点击华为账号登录或者只用微信、QQ、微博登录</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105300072163123776=\"100\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7f_yslgw.jpg\"><img width=\"260\" height=\"440\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f7f_yslgw.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2.找回账号后，若发现华为穿戴APP中管理员管号码已经为空，可以编辑自己的信息，重新设置并验证手机号，就可以完成号码找回。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><strong>lAPP登录后，界面上提示“未能连接手表”</strong></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">APP上提示“未能连接手表”或手表定位不刷新，请按以下步骤操作：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp; 请用户确认手表是否欠费或者关机。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">若手表是关机状态，请按手表侧键3s开启手表之后，点击APP右上角的手动定位刷新。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">若手表欠费，请用户缴纳费用后，长按手表侧键10S重启手表。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp; 排除以上两种情况仍无法刷新定，请确认手表信号格后是否有上下行箭头+红色查查，如果有请用户长按手表侧键10S重启手表或取出SIM卡重新安装，再长按手表侧键10s重启手表。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp; 若始终提示“未能连接手表”或反复提示“未能连接手，请用户反馈手表IMEI号、手表版本号，上升研发处理。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a jQuery17105300072163123776=\"112\" href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f87_hvdc7.jpg\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"462\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f87_hvdc7.jpg\"></a></p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1546","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444265810000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":70,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,配对,配对失败,无法配对,绑定,绑定失败,无法绑定","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}